OL,6,FAfter losing her 16-year-old daughter,
OL,7,FBrodie, to suicide Emma Webb has made
OL,8,Fit her life's mission to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of mental health and suicide
OL,10,Fprevention.
OL,12,FShe is one of four inspiring
OL,13,Findividuals in Wales who've been
OL,14,Fnominated for the Pride of Britain
OL,15,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year award.
