OL,3,CMum walks nearly 300 miles in memory
OL,4,Cof daughter lost to suicide
OL,6,FIn 2021 Emma raised more than #10,000
OL,7,Ffor the prevention of young suicide
OL,8,Fcharity, Papyrus, walking over 285
OL,9,Fmiles, one mile for each of the 285
OL,10,Flives lost to suicide in the previous
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FHer next challenge was a tribute to
OL,14,Fher daughter Brodie's love of horses.
OL,16,FEmma hauled a life-size resin horse
OL,17,Fshe called Miles, from Chepstow to
OL,18,FLondon.
