OL,4,Cof daughter lost to suicide
OL,6,FThe money raised was for Papyrus and
OL,7,FRiders Minds, an equestrian mental
OL,8,Fhealth charity.
OL,10,FOn the way she had a surprise visit
OL,11,Ffrom Prince William.
OL,13,F"He just jumped right from behind the
OL,14,Fhorse and said 'Boo!' ," she said
OL,16,F"It was just an unbelievable moment.
OL,17,FI'm so grateful for the support that
OL,18,FPrince William gave me.
