OL,3,CMum walks nearly 300 miles in memory
OL,4,Cof daughter lost to suicide
OL,6,F"He walked along with us for 25
OL,7,Fminutes, shoulder to shoulder, pushing
OL,8,Fthe horse. And we chatted about mental
OL,9,Fhealth, about Brodie's story. Prince
OL,10,FWilliam told me how important mental
OL,11,Fhealth was to him as well."
OL,13,FLater this month she plans to walk
OL,14,Ffrom Newport to Birmingham NEC to
OL,15,Fappear at the Horse of the Year Show.
OL,17,F"It's quite hilly this time, so it
OL,18,Fwill be challenging so I'm hoping by
OL,19,Fthe time I get to Birmingham that I
OL,20,Fwill have smashed the hundred thousand
OL,21,Fpounds barrier," Emma said.
