OL,3,CMum walks nearly 300 miles in memory
OL,4,Cof daughter lost to suicide
OL,6,F"It always will be my purpose to and
OL,7,Fcarry on raising awareness and trying
OL,8,Fto help young people with mental
OL,9,Fwellbeing or thoughts of suicide."
OL,11,FEmma has a campaign running called
OL,12,FDoItForBrodie where she has decorated
OL,13,Fhorseshoes with charms and poems as
OL,14,Fwell as QR codes to a website which
OL,15,Fprovides links to charities.
OL,17,FShe says: 'I do it for Brodie, you
OL,18,Fknow. It is my of way of showing Brody
OL,19,Fall that love I have for her.'
